(50, 1, 'Christian JEQUEL was born January 16, 1935 in Ganges in the Cevennes.\r\nFrom 1958 he frequents assiduously Péano famous meeting place of the painters of Provence, called more commonly school of Rive Neuve. He discovers knife painting, develops his own technique and becomes one of the undisputed masters.'),
(50, 2, 'Christian JEQUEL于1935年1月16日出生于Cevennes的恒河。\r\n从1958年起，他经常光顾Péano着名的普罗旺斯画家聚会场所，这里更常见的是Rive Neuve学校。他发现刀画，发展自己的技术，成为无可争议的大师之'),
(51, 1, 'Jean-Marc JANIACZYK was born in 1966 in Douai in the north of France, he painted exclusively in oil since 1990, he began with a technically difficult style; hyperrealism.\r\nIt was in 1998 that he began painting with a knife, since he mainly paints Provençal landscapes, with vibrant and intense colors. From his paintings emerges, the light and the soft heat of summers in Provence.'),
(51, 2, 'Jean-Marc JANIACZYK于1966年出生于法国北部的杜埃（Douai），自1990年以来一直专注于石油，他从技术上艰难的风格开始;超写实。\r\n1998年，他开始用刀子绘画，因为他主要绘制普罗旺斯风景画，色彩鲜明而浓烈。从他的画作出现，普罗旺斯夏天的光和温暖。'),
(52, 1, 'Born in 1957 in Alès, Michel VEZINET began painting in 1972. For more than 30 years, he has exhibited in numerous galleries both in France and abroad.\r\nThe artist has been painting with a knife since the age of 13; that is to say, he had time to refine his technique which he now has all the wheels.'),
(52, 2, 'Michel VEZINET于1957年出生于Alès，于1972年开始绘画。30多年来，他曾在法国和国外的众多画廊展出。\r\n这位艺术家从13岁开始就用刀子画画;也就是说，他有时间改进他现在拥有所有车轮的技术。'),
(53, 1, 'Franco-Swiss, born on 7/12/46, Richard Moisan settled in 1998 on the Côte d\'Azur. He presented a happy provencal painting, frank colors and blooming. His paintings were themed Luberon, but also the landscapes of the seaside and bouquets of bright flowers. While his personal galleries were located in Cannes and Vallauris, he also exhibited at Palm Desert, Munich, Luxembourg, Vienna, and France.'),
(53, 2, 'Franco-Swiss出生于7月12日/ 46日，Richard Moisan于1998年在Côted\'Azur定居。他展示了一幅快乐的普罗旺斯绘画，鲜艳的色彩和绽放。他的画作以Luberon为主题，也有海边的风景和鲜艳的花束。虽然他的个人画廊位于戛纳和瓦洛里斯，但他还在棕榈沙漠，慕尼黑，卢森堡，维也纳和法国展出。'),
(54, 1, 'Born in 1948, landscape sun, Kerfily pays tribute especially to Provence, Corsica, Luberon and the same cult to Brittany in a constant concern for color and light.\r\nProfessional training shared between artistic photography, visual arts and engraving.\r\nIn 1972, he exhibited his first works in Paris, then at the Museums of Modern Art, BOCHUM, MUNSTER and TREVES in Germany.'),
(54, 2, '出生于1948年的景观阳光，Kerfily特别向普罗旺斯，科西嘉，吕贝隆和布列塔尼的崇拜者致敬，他们一直关注色彩和光线。\r\n艺术摄影，视觉艺术和雕刻之间共享的专业培训。\r\n1972年，他在巴黎展出了他的第一部作品，然后在德国的现代艺术博物馆，BOCHUM，MUNSTER和TREVES展出。'),
(55, 1, 'Lucile CALLEGARI shares her time of life and work between Bordeaux and Paris.\r\nSelf-taught painter, revealed 8 years ago, it is in the world of history and art that she evolves since childhood. The creative community is enthusiastic about it, but it is only 35 years later that it finally opens up and unfolds violently and intimately.'),
(55, 2, 'Lucile CALLEGARI分享她在波尔多和巴黎之间的生活和工作时光。\r\n自学成才的画家，在8年前揭晓，从童年开始，它就在历史和艺术的世界里。创意社区对此充满热情，但仅仅35年后，它终于开放并且暴力和亲密地展开。'),
(56, 1, 'In the Quebec City region and surrounding areas, she has participated in various artistic events, including Art Battles for the Galerie D\'Art Factory, the Baie-Comeau Symposium, the Arts and Reflections Symposium, live performances including one for the Benefit evening of the Musée des Beaux-Arts in Quebec, another for La Télé D\'ici and for various private events.'),
(56, 2, '在魁北克市及周边地区，她参加了各种艺术活动，包括Galerie D\'艺术工厂的艺术战，Baie-Comeau研讨会，艺术和反思研讨会，现场表演，包括一个受益于魁北克MuséedesBeaux-Arts的晚会，LaTéléD\'ici的另一场活动以及各种私人活动。'),
(57, 1, 'Painter decorator in the poster and the decor of cinema, the artistic signs and the advertisement since 1964, the passion of the painting never left Gilbert THOMAS. Hiking and climbing in the creeks he has cruised back and forth since his childhood, a paradise on land and sea, are at the origin of his first paintings.'),
(57, 2, '画家装饰在海报和电影的装饰，艺术标志和广告自1964年以来，绘画的激情从未离开吉尔伯特托马斯。他小时候来回巡游的小溪徒步旅行和登山，是陆地和海洋的天堂，是他第一幅画作的起源。');
