(251, 1, 'Kurt Cobain', 'This work is a painting of the famous Kurt Cobain, the idea was to appropriate the traits of a personality and make it perceptible in another way, with a personal play of light and a play of colors to bring life to the portrait with new lighting. In a new dimension'),
(251, 2, 'Kurt Cobain', '这幅作品是着名的Kurt Cobain的一幅画，其理念是适应个性的特征，让它以另一种方式感知，通过个人的光线和色彩的运用，为画像带来生命。新的照明。在一个新的方面'),
(252, 1, 'king of pop', 'This work represents the lightness of pop king Michael Jackson. One of his famous dance steps that shows us all the grandeur and at the same time all the melancholy in this work.'),
(252, 2, '流行音乐之王', '这部作品代表了流行之王迈克尔·杰克逊的轻盈。他着名的舞步之一向我们展示了所有的壮丽，同时也展现了这部作品的所有忧郁。'),
(253, 1, 'Michael Jackson, the portrait', 'This work is a painting that represents the famous Michael Jackson. This portrait has an incredible resemblance, the brushstrokes at once fine and soft highlight the talent of the artist to capture this legend.'),
(253, 2, '迈克尔杰克逊，肖像', '这幅作品是代表着名迈克尔杰克逊的一幅画。这幅肖像具有令人难以置信的相似之处，一次又一次精致柔和的笔触突出了艺术家捕捉这一传奇的才华。'),
(254, 1, 'Bob Marley, cartoon', 'This work is a drawing by a young artist, representing Bob Marley.\r\nHere we see the street and modern graphic style that suits very well to this great artist that everyone loves.'),
(254, 2, '鲍勃马利，卡通', '这部作品是一位年轻艺术家的作品，代表鲍勃马利。\r\n在这里，我们看到街头和现代的图形风格，非常适合每个人都喜欢的伟大的艺术家。'),
(255, 1, 'Arman, Guitar', 'This work is an abacal sculpture, bronze with brown patina. It represents a guitar with an abstract and methodical style at the same time. The is all the contradiction that this work represents.'),
(255, 2, '阿曼，吉他', '这件作品是一个abacal雕塑，青铜色，棕色铜绿。它代表了一种具有抽象和有条理风格的吉他。这就是这项工作所代表的矛盾。'),
(256, 1, 'Sparkling duo', 'This work is an absolutely magnificent copper sculpture. It represents all the gypsy culture with this gypsy representation of a duet that plunges us into this particular universe.'),
(256, 2, '闪闪发光的二重奏', '这件作品是绝对华丽的铜雕。它代表了所有吉普赛文化，这种吉普赛表现了二重唱，让我们陷入这个特殊的宇宙。'),
(257, 1, 'Guitar and melody', 'This work is a set of several paintings that once assembled represents the music and its happiness. One could almost believe that the instruments painted here are alive and that they dance on the path drawn by the melody.'),
(257, 2, '吉他和旋律', '这部作品是一组曾经组装过的几幅画，代表着音乐及其快乐。人们几乎可以相信这里绘制的乐器是活着的，并且他们在旋律绘制的路径上跳舞。'),
(258, 1, 'Fusion and violin', 'This work is an abstract sculpture representing someone playing the violin. One could believe that the man merges with the instrument, that he becomes one with the music.'),
(258, 2, '融合和小提琴', '这件作品是一个代表有人拉小提琴的抽象雕塑。人们可以相信这个人与乐器合并，他与音乐成为一体'),
(259, 1, 'Venice musical trip', 'This work is a canvas made with oil with a brush and a knife. Everyone knows that Venice is one of the most romantic cities in the world and the artist wanted to highlight this beautiful city and music from piano to violin.'),
(259, 2, '威尼斯音乐之旅', '这件作品是用油刷和刀子制成的帆布。每个人都知道威尼斯是世界上最浪漫的城市之一，艺术家想要突出这个美丽的城市和音乐，从钢琴到小提琴。'),
(260, 1, 'two jazz man plays New York', 'This work is a drawing representing 2 jazzman in New York. The author puts forward the Jazz in New York which has a great history through these two men.'),
(260, 2, '两个爵士乐男子扮演纽约', '这幅作品代表了纽约的两位爵士乐手。作者提出了纽约的爵士乐，通过这两个人有着悠久的历史。'),
(261, 1, 'Portrait of Elvis Presley', 'This work is a painting of the Elvis king. The author wanted to represent Elvis with warm colors and this style of his own. The deep look of the king thinking of music makes one shudder.'),
(261, 2, '埃尔维斯普雷斯利的肖像', '这件作品是埃尔维斯国王的一幅画。作者希望以温暖的色彩和他自己的风格代表猫王。国王对音乐的深刻思考让人不寒而栗。'),
(262, 1, 'devil\'s clarinet', 'This work is a sculpture made of stone. You can see the head of a man and his hands playing a furious air. We can see the great precision of the artist on this work.'),
(262, 2, '魔鬼的单簧管', '这件作品是用石头砌成的雕塑。你可以看到一个男人的头和他的手在播放愤怒的空气。我们可以看到艺术家在这项工作中的精确度。'),
(263, 1, 'Johnny Halliday', 'This work represents Johnny Halliday. The technique of the artist is unique so that it is impossible not to recognize it in each of the galleries where it exposes. It starts with a collage, a print at the corner of a page can be the beginning of a canvas, it then mixes acrylic.'),
(263, 2, 'Johnny Halliday', '这项工作代表Johnny Halliday。艺术家的技术是独一无二的，因此不可能在每个展示的画廊中识别它。它以拼贴画开始，页面一角的印刷品可以是画布的开头，然后混合丙烯酸'),
(264, 1, 'Piano in color', 'This work is a painting done with a brush. Many hot colors that give warmth to an instrument that is usually considered sad.'),
(264, 2, '钢琴的颜色', '这件作品是用画笔完成的。许多热的颜色给仪器带来温暖，通常被认为是悲伤的。'),
(265, 1, 'gramophone', 'This work is a drawing made with a lot of precision. It represents the gramophone, instrument almost used more. The artist demonstrates well in the colors and the way of drawing that it is something old.'),
(265, 2, '留声机', '这项工作是一个精确的绘图。它代表留声机，仪器几乎使用更多。艺术家在颜色和绘画方式上表现得很好，这是一种古老的东西。'),
(266, 1, 'Portrait of Kendrick Lamar', 'This work is a painting of Kendrick Lamar, an American rapper.\r\nKendrick Lamar is the first rapper to win the Pulitzer Prize. The artist used several paintings to realize his work.'),
(266, 2, '肯德里克拉马尔的肖像', '这部作品是美国说唱歌手肯德里克拉玛的画作。\r\n肯德里克·拉马尔是第一位赢得普利策奖的说唱歌手。艺术家用几幅画来实现他的作品。'),
(267, 1, 'Mozart', 'This work is a painting of the nineteenth century. She represents the famous Wolfgang\r\nAmadeus Mozart. It is an old painting still very well preserved. She represents a genius of music.'),
(267, 2, 'Mozart', '这部作品是十九世纪的一幅画。她代表着名的沃尔夫冈\r\n艾玛迪斯莫扎特。这是一幅保存完好的旧画。她代表了一种音乐天才。'),
(268, 1, 'Ray Charles', 'This work is a painting on canvas embodying Ray Charles the famous American singer. The artist wanted to transmit to us his passion for this great gentleman considered for many as a genius of music.'),
(268, 2, '雷查尔斯', '这部作品是画布上的一幅画，体现了美国着名歌手雷·查尔斯。艺术家想要向我们传达他对这位伟大绅士的热情，这位绅士被认为是许多音乐天才。'),
(269, 1, 'The getaway of music', 'This work is a painting that represents the imagination. The artist brings us into his melancholic and magical world with animals of music and nature. A work full of originality.'),
(269, 2, '音乐之旅', '这幅作品是一幅代表想象力的画作。艺术家带着我们进入他充满音乐和自然的动物的忧郁和神奇的世界。一部充满创意的作品。'),
(270, 1, 'Violin woman', 'This work is a painting on canvas representing the mixture of a violin and a woman. The silouette and curves of a woman are reminiscent of the shape of a violin and the artist interprets it very well.'),
(270, 2, '小提琴的女人', '这幅作品是画布上的一幅画，代表了小提琴和女人的混合体。女人的silouette和曲线让人想起小提琴的形状，艺术家很好地解释了它。'),
(271, 1, 'Brassens', 'This work is a painting that represents one of the legends of French music, George Brassens. The artist takes us to his colorful world and shows great originality.'),
(271, 2, 'Brassens', '这幅作品是一幅代表法国音乐传奇人物乔治·布拉森斯的画作。艺术家将我们带到他丰富多彩的世界，展现出极佳的创意。'),
(272, 1, 'Contemporary violoncello', 'This work is a metal sculpture of contemporary modern art. It represents a violloncellist assembled with original materials. It plunges us into a universe so special.'),
(272, 2, '当代大提琴', '这件作品是当代现代艺术的金属雕塑，代表着用原始材料组装的violloncellist。它让我们陷入如此特殊的宇宙。'),
(273, 1, 'Monkey in music', 'This work is a painting of a monkey who listens to music with a headphone. It\'s modern yet daring yet provocative. This adds a spicy side to this work that makes the success of this work.'),
(273, 2, '猴子在音乐中', '这部作品是一幅用耳机听音乐的猴子画。它既现代又大胆又具有挑衅性。这为这项工作增添了辛辣的一面，使这项工作取得了成功。'),
(274, 1, 'Street music', 'This work is a painting with brush strokes very particular and original.\r\nShe represents a street musician who under his hat plays a guitar tune. We all knew a street musician who made us dream during our holidays. The artist reminds us of this particular feeling.'),
(274, 2, '街头音乐', '这件作品是一幅非常特别和原创的画笔。\r\n她代表一位街头音乐家，他戴着帽子弹吉他。我们都认识一位街头音乐家，他们在假期里让我们梦想成真。艺术家提醒我们这种特殊的感觉。'),
(275, 1, 'Vinyls and pop', 'This work is a painting representing music in itself with vinyls that make us think of the 90s. It is a contemporary work that strongly reminds us of the streets of San Francisco via Manhattan.'),
(275, 2, '乙烯基和流行音乐', '这幅作品是一幅用乙烯基代表音乐的画作，让我们想起90年代。这是一部当代作品，强烈地提醒我们通过曼哈顿的旧金山街道。'),
(276, 1, 'Jazz music', 'This work is a drawing representing pure jazz. The artist plunges us into the wild nights of the big American cities that lives to the rhythm of jazz played in bars, from piano to saxophone.'),
(276, 2, '爵士音乐', '这部作品是一幅代表纯粹爵士乐的作品。艺术家让我们沉浸在美国大城市的狂野之夜，这些城市生活在爵士乐的节奏中，从钢琴到萨克斯管。'),
(277, 1, 'jazz group men', 'This work is a painting on canvas made with a particular technique that can be seen in the brush strokes. She represents a group of Jazz in the 90s that reminds us of these bars full of music and emotions.'),
(277, 2, '爵士乐队男子', '这件作品是画布上的一幅画，用一种特殊的技术制作，可以在画笔笔划中看到。她代表着一群90年代的爵士乐队，让我们想起这些充满音乐和情感的酒吧。'),
(278, 1, 'Sweet violin', 'This work is a painting depicting a man playing the violin peacefully. The softness that emerges from this work is incredible and the artist really plunges us into his universe.'),
(278, 2, '甜小提琴', '这幅作品描绘的是一个男人和平地拉小提琴。这件作品带来的柔和感令人难以置信，艺术家真的让我们陷入了他的宇宙。'),
(279, 1, 'Hip hop', 'This work is a painting representing the art of street graffiti. A modern art that is very popular in recent years. Hip hop is the street music by excellence which goes very well to this art.'),
(279, 2, '嘻哈', '这幅作品是一幅代表街头涂鸦艺术的画作。近年来非常流行的现代艺术。嘻哈是卓越的街头音乐，非常适合这种艺术。'),
(280, 1, 'Eminem', 'This work is a painting representing the art of street graffiti. A modern art that is very popular in recent years. Hip hop is the street music by excellence which goes very well to this art.'),
(280, 2, 'Eminem', '这幅作品是一幅代表街头涂鸦艺术的画作。近年来非常流行的现代艺术。嘻哈是卓越的街头音乐，非常适合这种艺术。'),
(281, 1, 'coysevox', 'This work is a stone sculpture representing a man playing the flute. It plunges us into ancient Greece where the melody of the flutes goes very well with nature.'),
(281, 2, 'coysevox', '这件作品是一个代表一个男人吹奏长笛的石头雕塑。它使我们陷入古希腊，在那里长笛的旋律与大自然非常吻合。'),
(282, 1, 'Musical wave', 'This work is a set of three painted paintings that assembled represents a sound effect. This representation of the musical flow plunges us into this little known world of music waves.'),
(282, 2, '音乐浪潮', '这件作品是一组三幅画作，组合起来代表了一种音效。音乐流的这种表现使我们陷入这个鲜为人知的音乐世界。'),
(283, 1, 'Stromae', 'This work is a painting done in acrylic that represents the Belgian singer\r\nStromae. The artist shows us here a style a little cartoon that goes very well to this singer who also has this naive almost childish style.'),
(283, 2, 'Stromae', '这件作品是用丙烯酸制作的画，代表比利时歌手\r\n司徒迈。艺术家向我们展示了一个风格，一个小卡通风格，非常适合这位歌手，他也有这种幼稚几乎幼稚的风格'),
(284, 1, 'Horn with two', 'This work is a very deep painting on canvas that depicts two men playing the horn. The horns are a wind instrument still unknown to the general public and the artist transports us into this universe.'),
(284, 2, '角有两个', '这幅作品是画布上非常深刻的画作，描绘了两个演奏号角的男人。喇叭是一种仍然不为公众所知的管乐器，艺术家将我们带入这个宇宙。'),
(285, 1, 'The Beatles', 'This work is a painting that has the characteristic of being very neat. She represents the legendary rock group of the Beatles and immerses us in the musical world of these very talented musicians and singers.'),
(285, 2, '披头士乐队', '这幅作品是一幅具有非常整洁特色的画作。她代表披头士乐队的传奇摇滚乐队，让我们沉浸在这些非常有才华的音乐家和歌手的音乐世界中'),
(286, 1, 'Far West', 'This work is a realistic drawing depicting country music in the western United States. This work plunges us into an array of color and feelings that can be found in the far west.'),
(286, 2, '狂野的西部', '这部作品是描绘美国西部乡村音乐的真实画作。这项工作让我们陷入了一系列的色彩和感情，可以在遥远的西方找到。'),
(287, 1, 'The cherry season', 'This work is a painting on canvas that represents the soft music of the violin associated with cherries, spring and all this melancholy. This mixture of colors allows in a second time to have a hypnotic effect on the viewer.'),
(287, 2, '樱桃的时间', '这幅作品是画布上的一幅画，代表了与樱桃，春天和所有这些忧郁相关的小提琴的柔和音乐。这种颜色混合允许第二次对观察者产生催眠效果。'),
(288, 1, 'piano at the water\'s edge', 'This work is an acrylic painting of a piano in the middle of the ocean. The romanticism of this work makes it an absolutely magical work to look at, with this magnificent moon and this incredible landscape plan.'),
(288, 2, '钢琴在水边', '这件作品是在海洋中间的钢琴丙烯画。这项工作的浪漫主义使得这个壮观的月亮和这个令人难以置信的景观规划看起来绝对神奇。'),
(289, 1, 'musical rocking', 'This work is a painting on canvas depicting an electric guitar. All the rock and roll of this work do something beautiful. The colors subjugate us and take us into this particular universe.'),
(289, 2, '音乐摇摆', '这幅作品是画布上描绘电吉他的画作。这项工作的所有摇滚乐都做得很漂亮。颜色征服了我们，把我们带入了这个特殊的宇宙。'),
(290, 1, 'Bass and roll', 'This work is a painting on canvas representing an undesirable instrument of rock, the electric bass. The artist wanted to represent the power of the bass, with bright colors.'),
(290, 2, '低音和滚动', '这幅作品是画布上的一幅画，代表了一种不受欢迎的摇滚乐器 - 电贝司。艺术家想要用鲜艳的色彩来表现低音的力量。');
